jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/david-gilmour@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-gilmour">大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour)</a>谈到了他即将推出的个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-returns-with-luck-and-strange-his-first-new-solo-album-in-nine-years-3750328">《Luck And Strange》</a> ，他将这张专辑与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">平克·弗洛伊德 (Pink Floyd</a> ) 的《月之暗面》(Dark Side Of The Moon) 进行了比较 - 看看他在下面怎么说。</p><p>吉尔摩在开始个人职业生涯之前曾是平克·弗洛伊德乐队 (Pink Floyd) 的著名成员，他在接受<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/news/pink-floyd-legend-david-gilmour-is-on-the-cover-of-the-new-issue-of-prog-on-sale-now"><em>Prog 杂志</em></a>（通过<a href="https://www.guitarworld.com/news/david-gilmour-luck-and-strange-dark-side-of-the-moon-comparisons" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《吉他世界</em></a>》）采访时谈到他即将发行的唱片：“距《月之暗面》已经过去 50 多年了。我的感觉是这张专辑是自 1973 年《The Dark Side Of The Moon》问世以来我多年来制作的最好的专辑。”</p><p>这是高度赞扬，因为在《月之暗面》之后，平克·弗洛伊德继续发行了《动物》和《墙》等经典作品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752393" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752393" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752393" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024.jpg" alt="大卫·吉尔莫（Matthew Eisman/Getty Images 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Gilmour-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752393" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·吉尔莫（Matthew Eisman/Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在与<em>Prog</em>的聊天中，吉尔莫开玩笑说他很快就会开始制作《Luck And Strange》的后续作品，并热切期待与专辑的几位合作者重聚：“我们的计划只是把这张专辑推出运行它，然后立即执行另一个。我将再次与所有这些人一起工作。”</p><p> 《幸运与奇异》定于 9 月 6 日发行，<a href="https://davidgilmour.lnk.to/LuckandStrange" target="_blank" rel="noopener">可在此处预订/预保存</a>。这张密纹唱片在布莱顿和伦敦录制了五个多月。他的妻子、作家兼作词家波莉·桑普森 (Polly Sampson) <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">此前曾记录过吉尔莫参观工作室的经历，并</a><a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">在她的个人 Instagram 上分享了这些照片</a>。</p><p>曲目列表包括八首全新曲目以及 Montgolfier Brothers 1999 年曲目“Between Two Points”的改编版。到目前为止，这张专辑已经预演了两首单曲“The Piper&#39;s Call”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-david-gilmour-and-daughter-romanys-whimsical-new-single-between-two-points-3766354">蒙哥菲尔兄弟与他的女儿 Romany Gilmour 一起重新创作的 1999 年歌曲“Between Two Points”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750339" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750339" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750339" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn.jpg" alt="大卫·吉尔莫黑白新闻照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbij